title: Calendar
description: A date field component that allows users to enter and edit date.

body.raw:
<ComponentPreview name="calendar-demo" />

## About

The `Calendar` component is built on top of [React DayPicker](https://react-day-picker.js.org).

## Installation

<Tabs defaultValue="cli">

<TabsList>
  <TabsTrigger value="cli">CLI</TabsTrigger>
  <TabsTrigger value="manual">Manual</TabsTrigger>
</TabsList>
<TabsContent value="cli">

```bash
npx shadcn-ui@latest add calendar
```

</TabsContent>

<TabsContent value="manual">

<Steps>

<Step>Install the following dependencies:</Step>

```bash
npm install react-day-picker date-fns
```

<Step>Add the `Button` component to your project.</Step>

The `Calendar` component uses the `Button` component. Make sure you have it installed in your project.

<Step>Copy and paste the following code into your project.</Step>

<ComponentSource name="calendar" />

<Step>Update the import paths to match your project setup.</Step>

</Steps>

</TabsContent>

</Tabs>

## Usage

```tsx
import { Calendar } from "@/components/ui/calendar"
```

```tsx
const [date, setDate] = React.useState<Date | undefined>(new Date())

return (
  <Calendar
    mode="single"
    selected={date}
    onSelect={setDate}
    className="rounded-md border"
  />
)
```

See the [React DayPicker](https://react-day-picker.js.org) documentation for more information.

## Date Picker

You can use the `<Calendar>` component to build a date picker. See the [Date Picker](/docs/components/date-picker) page for more information.

## Examples

### Form

\r
import * as React from "react"\r
import { ChevronLeft, ChevronRight } from "lucide-react"\r
import { DayPicker } from "react-day-picker"\r
\r
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils"\r
import { buttonVariants } from "@/components/ui/button"\r
\r
export type CalendarProps = React.ComponentProps<typeof DayPicker>\r
\r
function Calendar({\r
  className,\r
  classNames,\r
  showOutsideDays = true,\r
  ...props\r
}: CalendarProps) {\r
  return (\r
    <DayPicker\r
      showOutsideDays={showOutsideDays}\r
      className={cn("p-3", className)}\r
      classNames={{\r
        months: "flex flex-col sm:flex-row space-y-4 sm:space-x-4 sm:space-y-0",\r
        month: "space-y-4",\r
        caption: "flex justify-center pt-1 relative items-center",\r
        caption_label: "text-sm font-medium",\r
        nav: "space-x-1 flex items-center",\r
        nav_button: cn(\r
          buttonVariants({ variant: "outline" }),\r
          "h-7 w-7 bg-transparent p-0 opacity-50 hover:opacity-100"\r
        ),\r
        nav_button_previous: "absolute left-1",\r
        nav_button_next: "absolute right-1",\r
        table: "w-full border-collapse space-y-1",\r
        head_row: "flex",\r
        head_cell:\r
          "text-muted-foreground rounded-md w-9 font-normal text-[0.8rem]",\r
        row: "flex w-full mt-2",\r
        cell: "h-9 w-9 text-center text-sm p-0 relative [&:has([aria-selected].day-range-end)]:rounded-r-md [&:has([aria-selected].day-outside)]:bg-accent/50 [&:has([aria-selected])]:bg-accent first:[&:has([aria-selected])]:rounded-l-md last:[&:has([aria-selected])]:rounded-r-md focus-within:relative focus-within:z-20",\r
        day: cn(\r
          buttonVariants({ variant: "ghost" }),\r
          "h-9 w-9 p-0 font-normal aria-selected:opacity-100"\r
        ),\r
        day_range_end: "day-range-end",\r
        day_selected:\r
          "bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary hover:text-primary-foreground focus:bg-primary focus:text-primary-foreground",\r
        day_today: "bg-accent text-accent-foreground",\r
        day_outside:\r
          "day-outside text-muted-foreground opacity-50 aria-selected:bg-accent/50 aria-selected:text-muted-foreground aria-selected:opacity-30",\r
        day_disabled: "text-muted-foreground opacity-50",\r
        day_range_middle:\r
          "aria-selected:bg-accent aria-selected:text-accent-foreground",\r
        day_hidden: "invisible",\r
        ...classNames,\r
      }}\r
      components={{\r
        IconLeft: ({ ...props }) => <ChevronLeft className="h-4 w-4" />,\r
        IconRight: ({ ...props }) => <ChevronRight className="h-4 w-4" />,\r
      }}\r
      {...props}\r
    />\r
  )\r
}\r
Calendar.displayName = "Calendar"\r
\r
export { Calendar }\r

\r
import * as React from "react"\r
import { ChevronLeftIcon, ChevronRightIcon } from "@radix-ui/react-icons"\r
import { DayPicker } from "react-day-picker"\r
\r
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils"\r
import { buttonVariants } from "@/registry/default/ui/button"\r
\r
export type CalendarProps = React.ComponentProps<typeof DayPicker>\r
\r
function Calendar({\r
  className,\r
  classNames,\r
  showOutsideDays = true,\r
  ...props\r
}: CalendarProps) {\r
  return (\r
    <DayPicker\r
      showOutsideDays={showOutsideDays}\r
      className={cn("p-3", className)}\r
      classNames={{\r
        months: "flex flex-col sm:flex-row space-y-4 sm:space-x-4 sm:space-y-0",\r
        month: "space-y-4",\r
        caption: "flex justify-center pt-1 relative items-center",\r
        caption_label: "text-sm font-medium",\r
        nav: "space-x-1 flex items-center",\r
        nav_button: cn(\r
          buttonVariants({ variant: "outline" }),\r
          "h-7 w-7 bg-transparent p-0 opacity-50 hover:opacity-100"\r
        ),\r
        nav_button_previous: "absolute left-1",\r
        nav_button_next: "absolute right-1",\r
        table: "w-full border-collapse space-y-1",\r
        head_row: "flex",\r
        head_cell:\r
          "text-muted-foreground rounded-md w-8 font-normal text-[0.8rem]",\r
        row: "flex w-full mt-2",\r
        cell: cn(\r
          "relative p-0 text-center text-sm focus-within:relative focus-within:z-20 [&:has([aria-selected])]:bg-accent [&:has([aria-selected].day-outside)]:bg-accent/50 [&:has([aria-selected].day-range-end)]:rounded-r-md",\r
          props.mode === "range"\r
            ? "[&:has(>.day-range-end)]:rounded-r-md [&:has(>.day-range-start)]:rounded-l-md first:[&:has([aria-selected])]:rounded-l-md last:[&:has([aria-selected])]:rounded-r-md"\r
            : "[&:has([aria-selected])]:rounded-md"\r
        ),\r
        day: cn(\r
          buttonVariants({ variant: "ghost" }),\r
          "h-8 w-8 p-0 font-normal aria-selected:opacity-100"\r
        ),\r
        day_range_start: "day-range-start",\r
        day_range_end: "day-range-end",\r
        day_selected:\r
          "bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary hover:text-primary-foreground focus:bg-primary focus:text-primary-foreground",\r
        day_today: "bg-accent text-accent-foreground",\r
        day_outside:\r
          "day-outside text-muted-foreground opacity-50  aria-selected:bg-accent/50 aria-selected:text-muted-foreground aria-selected:opacity-30",\r
        day_disabled: "text-muted-foreground opacity-50",\r
        day_range_middle:\r
          "aria-selected:bg-accent aria-selected:text-accent-foreground",\r
        day_hidden: "invisible",\r
        ...classNames,\r
      }}\r
      components={{\r
        IconLeft: ({ ...props }) => <ChevronLeftIcon className="h-4 w-4" />,\r
        IconRight: ({ ...props }) => <ChevronRightIcon className="h-4 w-4" />,\r
      }}\r
      {...props}\r
    />\r
  )\r
}\r
Calendar.displayName = "Calendar"\r
\r
export { Calendar }\r

`,(0,n.jsxDEV)(p,{name:"calendar-form",children:[(0,n.jsxDEV)(e.div,{"data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment":"",children:(0,n.jsxDEV)(e.pre,{"data-language":"tsx","data-theme":"default",__rawString__:`"use client"\r
\r
import { zodResolver } from "@hookform/resolvers/zod"\r
import { format } from "date-fns"\r
import { CalendarIcon } from "lucide-react"\r
import { useForm } from "react-hook-form"\r
import * as z from "zod"\r
\r
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils"\r
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"\r
import { Calendar } from "@/components/ui/calendar"\r
import {\r
  Form,\r
  FormControl,\r
  FormDescription,\r
  FormField,\r
  FormItem,\r
  FormLabel,\r
  FormMessage,\r
} from "@/components/ui/form"\r
import {\r
  Popover,\r
  PopoverContent,\r
  PopoverTrigger,\r
} from "@/components/ui/popover"\r
import { toast } from "@/components/ui/use-toast"\r
\r
const FormSchema = z.object({\r
  dob: z.date({\r
    required_error: "A date of birth is required.",\r
  }),\r
})\r
\r
export function CalendarForm() {\r
  const form = useForm<z.infer<typeof FormSchema>>({\r
    resolver: zodResolver(FormSchema),\r
  })\r
\r
  function onSubmit(data: z.infer<typeof FormSchema>) {\r
    toast({\r
      title: "You submitted the following values:",\r
      description: (\r
        <pre className="mt-2 w-[340px] rounded-md bg-slate-950 p-4">\r
          <code className="text-white">{JSON.stringify(data, null, 2)}</code>\r
        </pre>\r
      ),\r
    })\r
  }\r
\r
  return (\r
    <Form {...form}>\r
      <form onSubmit={form.handleSubmit(onSubmit)} className="space-y-8">\r
        <FormField\r
          control={form.control}\r
          name="dob"\r
          render={({ field }) => (\r
            <FormItem className="flex flex-col">\r
              <FormLabel>Date of birth</FormLabel>\r
              <Popover>\r
                <PopoverTrigger asChild>\r
                  <FormControl>\r
                    <Button\r
                      variant={"outline"}\r
                      className={cn(\r
                        "w-[240px] pl-3 text-left font-normal",\r
                        !field.value && "text-muted-foreground"\r
                      )}\r
                    >\r
                      {field.value ? (\r
                        format(field.value, "PPP")\r
                      ) : (\r
                        <span>Pick a date</span>\r
                      )}\r
                      <CalendarIcon className="ml-auto h-4 w-4 opacity-50" />\r
                    </Button>\r
                  </FormControl>\r
                </PopoverTrigger>\r
                <PopoverContent className="w-auto p-0" align="start">\r
                  <Calendar\r
                    mode="single"\r
                    selected={field.value}\r
                    onSelect={field.onChange}\r
                    disabled={(date) =>\r
                      date > new Date() || date < new Date("1900-01-01")\r
                    }\r
                    initialFocus\r
                  />\r
                </PopoverContent>\r
              </Popover>\r
              <FormDescription>\r
                Your date of birth is used to calculate your age.\r
              </FormDescription>\r
              <FormMessage />\r
            </FormItem>\r
          )}\r
        />\r
        <Button type="submit">Submit</Button>\r
      </form>\r
    </Form>\r
  )\r
}\r

\r
import { zodResolver } from "@hookform/resolvers/zod"\r
import { CalendarIcon } from "@radix-ui/react-icons"\r
import { format } from "date-fns"\r
import { useForm } from "react-hook-form"\r
import * as z from "zod"\r
\r
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils"\r
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"\r
import { Calendar } from "@/components/ui/calendar"\r
import {\r
  Form,\r
  FormControl,\r
  FormDescription,\r
  FormField,\r
  FormItem,\r
  FormLabel,\r
  FormMessage,\r
} from "@/components/ui/form"\r
import {\r
  Popover,\r
  PopoverContent,\r
  PopoverTrigger,\r
} from "@/components/ui/popover"\r
import { toast } from "@/components/ui/use-toast"\r
\r
const FormSchema = z.object({\r
  dob: z.date({\r
    required_error: "A date of birth is required.",\r
  }),\r
})\r
\r
export function CalendarForm() {\r
  const form = useForm<z.infer<typeof FormSchema>>({\r
    resolver: zodResolver(FormSchema),\r
  })\r
\r
  function onSubmit(data: z.infer<typeof FormSchema>) {\r
    toast({\r
      title: "You submitted the following values:",\r
      description: (\r
        <pre className="mt-2 w-[340px] rounded-md bg-slate-950 p-4">\r
          <code className="text-white">{JSON.stringify(data, null, 2)}</code>\r
        </pre>\r
      ),\r
    })\r
  }\r
\r
  return (\r
    <Form {...form}>\r
      <form onSubmit={form.handleSubmit(onSubmit)} className="space-y-8">\r
        <FormField\r
          control={form.control}\r
          name="dob"\r
          render={({ field }) => (\r
            <FormItem className="flex flex-col">\r
              <FormLabel>Date of birth</FormLabel>\r
              <Popover>\r
                <PopoverTrigger asChild>\r
                  <FormControl>\r
                    <Button\r
                      variant={"outline"}\r
                      className={cn(\r
                        "w-[240px] pl-3 text-left font-normal",\r
                        !field.value && "text-muted-foreground"\r
                      )}\r
                    >\r
                      {field.value ? (\r
                        format(field.value, "PPP")\r
                      ) : (\r
                        <span>Pick a date</span>\r
                      )}\r
                      <CalendarIcon className="ml-auto h-4 w-4 opacity-50" />\r
                    </Button>\r
                  </FormControl>\r
                </PopoverTrigger>\r
                <PopoverContent className="w-auto p-0" align="start">\r
                  <Calendar\r
                    mode="single"\r
                    selected={field.value}\r
                    onSelect={field.onChange}\r
                    disabled={(date) =>\r
                      date > new Date() || date < new Date("1900-01-01")\r
                    }\r
                    initialFocus\r
                  />\r
                </PopoverContent>\r
              </Popover>\r
              <FormDescription>\r
                Your date of birth is used to calculate your age.\r
              </FormDescription>\r
              <FormMessage />\r
            </FormItem>\r
          )}\r
        />\r
        <Button type="submit">Submit</Button>\r
      </form>\r
    </Form>\r
  )\r
}\r
